{
  "text": "The quadratic form (8) is obtained expanding the system Hamiltonian to second order around the average numbers of particles in components a and b,N a andN b , both equal to N/2 for the initial state (2) [CITATION_1] [CITATION_2] . χ is thus the derivative of the chemical potential with respect to the particle number in each",
